#~ "## Wiki <a id=\"wiki\"></a>\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "Please refer to the wiki at <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki\">https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki</a> for more documentation.\n"
